@{
    ViewBag.Title = "SchoolsProgramme";
    Layout = "~/Views/_LayoutPage.cshtml";
}

<link href="@Url.Content("~/CSS/BookingButtons.css")" rel="stylesheet" />

<!--=== Content Part ===-->
<div class="container content">
    <div class="headline"><h2>Our Schools Programme</h2></div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-9">

            <div class="col-md-4 margin-bottom-25">
                <img class="img-responsive" src="@Url.Content("~/img/schoolspic1.jpg")" alt="" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 margin-bottom-25">
                <img class="img-responsive" src="@Url.Content("~/img/schoolspic2.jpg")" alt="" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 margin-bottom-25">
                <img class="img-responsive" src="@Url.Content("~/img/schoolspic3.jpg")" alt="" />
            </div>

            <p>
                We believe passionately about making tennis more accessible for all. We provide opportunities for children and young people to get involved in the game through our school-club links.
            </p>

            <p>
                What can we offer local schools?
                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                    <li><i class="fa fa-check color-green"></i>	FREE taster sessions during school hours with our LTA qualified coaches</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-check color-green"></i>	An Out of School Hours Tennis Club</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-check color-green"></i>	An invitation to our annual Primary Schools Festival</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-check color-green"></i>	Awareness of sessions and activities at our club for pupils and their families</li>
                </ul>
            </p>
            <p>
                What are the benefits for the school?
                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                    <li><i class="fa fa-check color-green"></i>	Increased opportunities for pupils at your school</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-check color-green"></i>	Raised profile of your school in the community</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-check color-green"></i>	Access for your pupils to top quality facilities and equipment</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-check color-green"></i>	Access to a team of qualified and experienced coaches, who can also support the development of teachers and school staff</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-check color-green"></i>	Healthier and more physically active pupils, which has been proven to improve concentration and behaviour in children.</li>
                </ul>
            </p>
            <p>

            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
            <!-- Contacts -->
            <div class="headline"><h2>Contact</h2></div>
            If you would like further information about how we can support your school please contact:
            <ul class="list-unstyled who margin-bottom-30">
                <li><a href="#"><i class="fa fa-home"></i>Schools development officer: Scott Davies</a></li>
                <li><a href="#"><i class="fa fa-envelope"></i>scott@tenniscoaching.london</a></li>
                <li><a href="#"><i class="fa fa-phone"></i>07777 645 628</a></li>
                <!--<li><a href="#"><i class="fa fa-globe"></i>http://www.example.com</a></li>-->
            </ul>
            <img class="img-responsive" src="@Url.Content("~/img/Aegon-schools-logo.jpg")" alt="" />
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="headline"><h2>View existing school links</h2></div>
    <div class="panel-group acc-v1 margin-bottom-40" id="accordion">
        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseOne">
                        Sunnyhill Primary School
                    </a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseOne" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    We run an after school tennis club for Sunnyhill pupils at the school site. The club is held on Tuesdays from 3:15 - 4:15pm.  

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseTwo">
                        Holy Ghost Primary School
                    </a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseTwo" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    We run an after school tennis club for Holy Ghost pupils at the school site. The club is for children in years 5 and 6 and is held on Mondays from 3:30 - 4:30pm.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseThree">
                        Streatham and Clapham High School
                    </a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseThree" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    We offer a large tennis programme at the school during the summer term. Girls can book via the school. Our involvement with the school extends
                     all year round and includes group coaching at Wigmore tennis club which are exclusively for girls from the school.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseFour">
                        Streatham and Clapham Junior School
                    </a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseFour" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    We run a breakfast club on Thursday mornings at the school. To join please apply via the school office.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseFive">
                        Rutherford House School
                    </a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseFive" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    We run a breakfast tennis club for Rutherford pupils at the school. The club is on Tuesdays (intermediate players in Year 1 and Year 2 - must have played tennis before) and Fridays beginners - players in reception, Year 1 and Year 2 who are new to tennis) from 08:00 - 08:45am.  The Spring Term 2016 is a 9 week course starting Tuesday 12th and Friday 15th January. The cost is £36.00 per player.
                    <br />
                    <a href="https://payableform.appspot.com/forms/ocgbx" class="Yellow">Book Spring 2016 (12th / 15th January start)</a>
                 

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseSix">
                        Furzedown Primary School
                    </a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseSix" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    We run an after school tennis club for Furzedown pupils at the school. The club is on Thursdays from 3:00 - 4:00pm. It’s open to years 1, 2 and 3 and will run for each half-term. To sign-up contact the school office.                    
                   
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">
                    <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseSeven">
                       Oliver House School
                    </a>
                </h4>
            </div>
            <div id="collapseSeven" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                <div class="panel-body">
                    We are pleased to now be the tennis provider for Oliver House School. 
                    Pupils will be attending Wigmore four days a week during 2016 term time.
                    

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
